from center for policy research cpr subject from israeli pres madnes from center for policy research cpr subject from israeli pres madnes written pm apr by cpr in igc from israeli pres madnes from the israeli pres paper zman tel aviv tel aviv time friday local tel aviv paper affiliate with maariv date february journalist guy ehrlich subject interview with soldier who serve in the duvdevan cherry unit which disguise themself a arab and operate within the occupy territory excerpt from the article a lot ha be write about the unit who disguise themself a arab thing good and bad some of the falsehood but the most important problem of those unit ha be hardly deal with it be that everyone who serve in the cherry after a time go in one way or another insane a man who say thi who will here be call danny hi full name be know to the editor serve in the cherry after hi discharge from the army he work a delivery boy hi pal who will here be call dudu wa also serve in the cherry and be now about to depart for a round-the-world tmy they both look no different from average israeli youngster freshly discharge from conscript service but in their soul one can notice something completely different it wa not easy for them to come out with disclosure about what happen to them and they think that to most of their fellow from the cherry it wind be easy either yet after they begin to talk it wa nearly impossible to make them stop talk the follow article will contain all the horror story recount with an appal opennes a short time ago i wa in command of a veteran team in which some of the fellow apply for release from the cherry we call such soldier by the intifada under my command wa a soldier who talk to himself non-stop which be a common phenomenon in the cherry i send him to a psychiatrist but why i should talk about other when i myself feel quite insane on friday when i come home my parent know i can not be talk to until i go to the beach surf a little calm down and return the key of my father car must be ready for in advance so that i can go there i they dare talk to me before or whenever i do want them to talk to me i just grab a chair and smash it instantly i know it be my nerve smashing chair all the time and then run away from home to the car and to the beach only there i become normal another friday i wa eat a lunch prepare by my mother it wa an omelette of sort she take the risk of sit next to me and talk to me i then tell my mother about an event which wa still fresh in my mind i tell her how i shoot an arab and how exactly hi wind look like when i go to inspect it she begin to laugh hysterically i want her to cry and she dare laugh straight in my face instead so i tell her how my pal have make a mincemeat of the two arab who be prepare the molotov cocktail he shoot them down hit them beautifully exactly a they deserve one bullet have set a molotov cocktail on fire with the effect that the arab wa burn all over just beautifully i wa delight to see it my pal fire three bullet two at the arab with the molotov cocktail and the third at hi chum it hit him straight in hi a we both felt that we pull off something next i tell my mother how another pal of mine split open the gut in the belly of another arab and how all of u run toward that spot to take a look i reach the spot first and then that arab blood gush forth from hi body spit at me i yell up and he dare talk back to me in hebrew so i just laugh straight in hi face i be usually laugh when i stare at something convulse right before my eye then i tell him right wait a moment i leave him in order to take a look at another wound arab i ask a soldier if that arab could be save if the bleed from hi artery could be stop with the help of a stone of something else like that i keep tell all thi to my mother with detail and she keep laugh straight into my face thi infuriate me i get very angry because i felt i wa become mad so i stop eat seize the plate with he omelette and some trim still on and at once throw it over her head only then she stop laugh at first she do know what to say but i must tell you of a still other madnes which fall upon u frequently i go with a friend to practice shoot on a field a gull appear right in the middle of the field my friend shoot it at once then we notice fmy deer stand high up on the hill above u my friend at once aim at one of them and shoot it we enjoy the sight of it fall down the rock we shoot down two deer more and go to take a look when we climb the rock we saw a young deer badly wound by my bullet but still try to such some milk from it already dead mother we carefully inspect two path cover by blood and chunk of tear flesh of the two deer we have hit we be just delight by that sight we have so good then we decide to kill the young deer too so a spare it further suffer i approach take out my revolver and shoot him in the head several time from a very short distance when you shoot straight at the head you actually see the bullet sink in but my fifth bullet make it brain fall outside onto the grind with the effect of splatter lot of blood straight on u thi make u feel cure of the spurt of my madnes standing there soak with blood we felt we be like beast of prey we could explain what have happen to u we be almost in tear while walk down from that hill and we felt the whole day very badly we alway go back to place we carry out assignment in thi be why we can see them when you see a guy you disable may be for the rest of hi life you feel you get power you feel godlike of sort both danny and dudu contemplate at least at thi moment study the act dudu be not will to work in any security-linked occupation danny feel the exact opposite should i take advantage of the skill i have master so well why should i earn for each chop head i would deliver while be a mercenary in south africa thi kind of job suit me perfectly i have no human emotion any more if i get a reasonable salary i will have no problem to board a plane to bosnium in order to fight there transl by israel shahak 